tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_url VARCHAR(255),
    user_id INT,
    user_age INT,
    user_gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE user_demographics (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic_sources (
    source_id INT,
    source_name VARCHAR(255),
    visit_count INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (source_id)
)

CREATE TABLE user_demographics (
    user_id INT,
    user_name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(255),
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
)

CREATE TABLE report_data (
    report_id INT,
    source_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    unique_visitors INT,
    pageviews INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (report_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (source_id) REFERENCES website_traffic_sources(source_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_demographics(user_id)
)
